data.description: Discover lakeside living in this prime location in the serene Arrowhead Lakes community of Glendale, Arizona! Offering an unparalleled blend of natural beauty and modern amenities, this home is a true oasis in the desert. Step into the spacious interior featuring 3 bedrooms and 2 well-appointed bathrooms, all designed to maximize comfort and convenience. The open-concept living area, graced with large windows with plantation shutters invites the breathtaking mountain views creating a seamless indoor-outdoor ambiance that's perfect for Arizona's lifestyle. The gourmet kitchen will inspire your culinary adventures, while the adjoining dining space is ideal for gatherings, both large and intimate. Retire to the primary suite which looks out over your private pool, spa, and lakeside dock!
